MIT License

This crate is a fork of `wezterm-char-props` from the WezTerm project,
reduced to the emoji presentation and variation-sequence data tables
that Rio needs for VS15/VS16 width handling. The data files
(`emoji_presentation.rs`, `emoji_variation.rs`) and the `Presentation`
API in `emoji.rs` are copied verbatim from WezTerm with only trivial
edits (module paths, header comments).

Upstream: https://github.com/wezterm/wezterm/tree/main/wezterm-char-props

